The Basque of the glossary: for mi presenta for ju biskusa eta sagarduna
The Icelandic of the glossary: Eg skal gefa þier braudkoku og Syrdryck
English translation: I will give you a biscuit and a sour drink

The Basque of the glossary: presenta for mi berrua usnia eta berria bura
Modern Basque: Emadazu esne beroa eta gurin berria
The Icelandic of the glossary: gefdu mier heita miölk og nyt smior
English translation: Give me hot milk and new butter
